Install npm
http://npmjs.org/install.sh

sudo sh install.sh

We need npm to install eventmachine to handle sockets

Use this README file to introduce your application and point to useful places in the API for learning more.
Run "rake doc:app" to generate API documentation for your models, controllers, helpers, and libraries.

If you create a new model with scaffold make sure you adapt to bootstrap css. 
	rails g boostrap:themed model_name

Delete any scaffold.css because this will afect any view into the app.
      <th><%= model_class.human_attribute_name(:inventory) %></th>
      <th><%= model_class.human_attribute_name(:sale_cost) %></th>
      <th><%= model_class.human_attribute_name(:utility_adjusment) %></th>
      <th><%= model_class.human_attribute_name(:lost_adjustment) %></th>
      <th><%= model_class.human_attribute_name(:income) %></th>
      <th><%= model_class.human_attribute_name(:sales_return) %></th>
      <th><%= model_class.human_attribute_name(:purchase_return) %></th>
      <th><%= model_class.human_attribute_name(:sale_tax) %></th>
      <th><%= model_class.human_attribute_name(:purchase_tax) %></th>


